radargig<-meanhouse[2:6,]
row.names(radargig)<-radargig[,1]
radargig<-radargig[,-(8:9)]
radargig<-radargig[,-(6:7)]
Name<-radargig[,1]
radargig<-radargig[,-(1)]
#
zradargig<-radargig
for(i in 1:length(radargig))
{
  zradargig[,i]<-(radargig[,i]-min(radargig[,i]))/(max(radargig[,i])-min(radargig[,i]))
}
zradargig<-data.frame(Name,zradargig)

library(knitr)
library(ggradar)
ggradar(zradargig,axis.label.size =8,grid.label.size = 18)
